Embeds


We've implemented new type 
embed
. 


This type has access to all 
documents
 in your 
project
.


Example: Countries 
 Cities


For example you have two collections 
countries
 and 
cities
.


Schema of 
countries


{
    "properties": {
        "name": {
            "type": "string",
            "required": true
        },
        "code": {
            "type": "string",
            "required": true
        },
        "representation": {
            "type": "string",
            "processors": [
                {
                    "name": "template",
                    "in": {
                        "context": {
                            "code": {
                                "source": "property",
                                "property": "code"
                            },
                            "name": {
                                "source": "property",
                                "property": "name"
                            }
                        },
                        "syntax": {
                            "source": "value",
                            "value": "handlebars"
                        },
                        "template_string": {
                            "source": "value",
                            "value": "{{code}} - {{name}}"
                        }
                    }
                }
            ]
        }
    }
}



Schema of 
cities
:


{
    "properties": {
        "name": {
            "type": "string"
        },
        "country": {
            "type": "embed",
            "collection": "countries",
            "field": "code"
        },
        "population": {
            "type": "number"
        }
    }
}



We have 
field
 property set pointing to 
code
.


Valid payloads to match are:






As a value:


{
   "country": "US"
}







As an object


{
    "country": {
        "code": "US"
    }
}







If you are not setting a 
field
 property filtering will be performed using a 
id
 field of a 
countries
 collection.


The result 
cities document
 with an embedded 
US
 country code as 
embed
 will be:


{
    "name": "Washington",
    "country": {
        "id": "united_states",
        "name": "United States",
        "code": "US",
        "representation": "US - United States"
    },
    "population": 321729000
}

