        "message": "",
        "errors": [
        ],
    }
}

Token permissions migrated from  {
    "permission": {
        "all": true,
        "read": [],
        "write": [],
        "delete": [],
        "update": []
    }
}  to   {
    "permission": {
        "allow": {
            "all": true,
            "read": [],
            "write": [],
            "delete": [],
            "update": []
        }
    }
}

System collections now have an underscore prefix. It's forbidden to create a collection with an underscore sign.  System fields  _id  now have an underscore prefix.  Response json interface  error  now is an array of objects. The schema is: {
    "property": {
        "type": ["string", "null"]
    },
    "message": {
        "type": "string"
    }
}
